Edward & Sons Brown Rice Snaps offer a blend of purity, simplicity, and wonderful taste. Since 1978, they have enhanced the table and delighted the palate of the most discerning natural gourmet. To create Brown Rice Snaps, 100% brown rice is carefully cleaned, and then milled into a fine flour containing the essential nutrients of the whole grain. Next, this whole grain rice flour is lightly steamed, kneaded, shaped, and oven-baked to golden perfection. Only choice, natural seasonings are added, such as wheat-free tamari, pure onion powder, or whole white sesame seeds. Savor the crispness, the flavor, and the elegance of Edward & Sons Brown Rice Snaps. The quality which you see and taste is just an indication of the care and concern behind this product. Rabbit of approval. Meet Bernie! Bernie was Annie's pet Dutch rabbit. When she started the company, Annie chose him to be our official rabbit of approval representing the simplicity, care, and goodness in all of our products. Dear Friend, In June 1974, my family packed our Chevy Malibu and drove from Connecticut to Leon, Mexico. We stayed at a small school where my father taught English during the summer. In an adobe-walled yard behind the school were 40 rabbits - los conejos. At twelve years old, I was ecstatic to be their caretaker. Since that summer, I've had many rabbits, but never dreamed I would have one that is nationally recognized like Bernie. Bye for now, Annie. Yum! And more yum! We partner with people & places we trust: to grow the organic wheat; to make flour for our Extra Cheesy Cheddar Bunnies and to raise the cows; to produce the milk for our cheese; to make your snack wonderfully wholesome & delicious.
